   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "160c530f-6dfb-40f2-9faa-8183b3ddad0c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Customer Reviews Sentiment Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "This project analyzes customer reviews to classify them into Negative, Neutral, and Positive sentiments. The text data is cleaned and transformed using TF-IDF, and a Logistic Regression model is used for classification.\n",
    "\n",
    "The model performance is evaluated using accuracy and confusion matrix. Additional features such as review date, score labels, and helpfulness metrics are created to support dashboard visualization in Power BI.\n",
    "\n",
    "The final output provides a structured dataset for sentiment analysis and business insights."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "25f22968-5fc6-48d2-be50-f0be514bc51e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Step 1: Importing libraries\n",
    "Importing all the libraries needed for data handling, text preprocessing, machine learning, and file export."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
